<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1408578-the-narrator-berkin-refers-to-vinny">The narrator (Berkin) refers to “Vinny” more than a few times in A Day in the Country...who/what/where is “Vinny”?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1408578'><a id="like_count_community_question_1408578" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1408578?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F60707.A_Month_in_the_Country">like</a></span>

