<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/1564654-mark"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1222373756i/1564654._UX100_CR0,16,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/1564654-mark">Mark</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Vinny is the narrator&apos;s (offscreen) wife. His fraught relationship with her seems to account for his sidelong mentions of her by name.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Vinny is the narrator's (offscreen) wife. His fraught relationship with her seems to account for his sidelong mentions of her by name.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
